<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Charlie Urbanowicz Home Page</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,300;0,8..60,400;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,300;1,8..60,400&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --cardinal: #CC0000;
  --cardinal-dark: #9B0000;
  --cardinal-deep: #5C0000;
  --gold: #C8922A;
  --gold-light: #E8B95A;
  --cream: #FAF7F2;
  --white: #FFFFFF;
  --ink: #1A1410;
  --ink-mid: #3D3028;
  --ink-light: #7A6A5A;
  --border: #DDD5C8;
  --pacific: #1B5E8A;
  --pacific-light: #3A8FC4;
  --section-gap: 56px;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

body {
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ── TOP STRIPE ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.top-stripe { background: var(--cardinal-deep); height: 5px; }

/* ── SITE HEADER ────────────────────────────────────── */
.site-header {
  background: var(--cardinal);
  padding: 0 32px;
}
.header-inner {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
  height: 50px;
}
.chico-wordmark {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
}
.chico-wordmark span { color: var(--gold-light); }
.hdr-div { width: 1px; height: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
.dept-label {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.07em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
}

/* ── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  background: var(--cardinal);
  position: relative;
  padding: 56px 32px 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 60px, rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 60px, rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 61px);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-content {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  align-items: end;
  padding-bottom: 88px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.hero-photo-wrap { position: relative; flex-shrink: 0; }
.hero-photo {
  width: 196px; height: 196px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  object-fit: cover;
  display: block;
  border: 4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
.hero-photo-accent {
  position: absolute; top: -8px; left: -8px;
  width: 196px; height: 196px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold);
  opacity: 0.55;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before {
  content: ''; display: inline-block;
  width: 26px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
}
.hero-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  line-height: 1.45;
}
.hero-meta {
  display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px 24px;
}
.meta-item {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
}
.meta-item a { color: var(--gold-light); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: border-color .2s; }
.meta-item a:hover { border-color: var(--gold-light); }
.hero-wave {
  position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 72px; overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-wave svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; }

/* ── DATE BANNER ────────────────────────────────────── */
.date-banner {
  background: var(--ink);
  padding: 14px 32px;
  text-align: center;
}
.date-banner p {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
}
.date-banner strong { color: var(--gold-light); }

/* ── RETIREMENT NOTICE ──────────────────────────────── */
.retirement-notice {
  background: #fff;
  border-left: 4px solid var(--cardinal);
  border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  padding: 18px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* ── LAYOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.page-wrap {
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 56px 32px 80px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 308px;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: start;
}

/* ── SECTION CHROME ─────────────────────────────────── */
.section { margin-bottom: var(--section-gap); }
.section:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.section-label {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--cardinal);
  margin-bottom: 5px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.section-label::after {
  content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border);
}
.section-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.section h4 {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin: 22px 0 10px;
}
.section p {
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  font-size: 15.5px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.section p b { color: var(--ink); }
.section p a { color: var(--cardinal); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(204,0,0,0.25); transition: border-color .2s; word-break: break-all; }
.section p a:hover { border-color: var(--cardinal); }

/* ── INTERESTS CARDS ────────────────────────────────── */
.interests-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.interest-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 18px 16px;
  transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s, border-color .2s;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.interest-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;
  width: 3px; height: 100%;
  background: var(--cardinal);
  transform: scaleY(0); transform-origin: bottom;
  transition: transform .25s;
}
.interest-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); border-color: #ccc; }
.interest-card:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }
.int-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 7px; display: block; line-height: 1; }
.int-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; font-style: italic;
  color: var(--cardinal); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 3px; display: block;
}
.int-title { font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.3; }

/* ── TIMELINE ───────────────────────────────────────── */
.timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.tl-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 88px 1fr;
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 22px;
}
.tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
.tl-item::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute;
  left: 88px; top: 9px; bottom: 0;
  width: 1px; background: var(--border);
}
.tl-item:last-child::after { display: none; }
.tl-year {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--cardinal);
  text-align: right; padding-right: 14px; padding-top: 2px;
}
.tl-body { padding-left: 18px; position: relative; }
.tl-body::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute;
  left: -4px; top: 8px;
  width: 8px; height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--cardinal);
  border: 2px solid var(--cream);
}
.tl-role { font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1px; }
.tl-org { font-size: 13.5px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-light); }

/* ── WEB PAGES LIST ─────────────────────────────────── */
.pages-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
.page-row {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 6px;
  padding: 14px 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
}
.page-row:hover { border-color: var(--cardinal); box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(204,0,0,0.07); }
.pg-badge {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #fff; background: var(--cardinal);
  border-radius: 3px; padding: 3px 7px;
  white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
}
.pg-badge.in-prog { background: var(--pacific); }
.pg-text strong { font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.pg-text a { font-size: 12px; color: var(--cardinal); text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; }
.pg-text a:hover { border-color: var(--cardinal); }
.pg-text em { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--ink-light); display: block; }

/* ── CV CALLOUT ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.cv-callout {
  background: var(--ink);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 22px 24px;
  margin: 28px 0;
}
.cv-callout p {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75) !important;
  font-size: 14.5px !important;
  margin-bottom: 14px !important;
}
.cv-callout p b { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95) !important; }
.cv-callout a { color: var(--gold-light) !important; border-color: rgba(232,185,90,0.3) !important; }
.cv-callout a:hover { border-color: var(--gold-light) !important; }

/* ── CRUISE SECTION ─────────────────────────────────── */
.cruise-header {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pacific) 0%, #0D3D5E 100%);
  border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
  padding: 28px 32px 24px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.cruise-header::after {
  content: '⚓'; position: absolute;
  right: 20px; bottom: -14px;
  font-size: 96px; opacity: 0.06; line-height: 1;
}
.cruise-header .section-label { color: var(--gold-light); }
.cruise-header .section-label::after { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
.cruise-header .section-title { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.cruise-header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.cruise-header p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.cruise-header b { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); }
.cruise-header a { color: var(--gold-light); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(232,185,90,0.35); }
.cruise-header a:hover { border-color: var(--gold-light); }
.cruise-header i { font-style: italic; }

.cruise-body {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-top: none;
  border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
  padding: 0;
  margin-bottom: var(--section-gap);
}
.cruise-entry {
  padding: 13px 24px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: baseline;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--ink-mid);
  transition: background .15s;
}
.cruise-entry:last-child { border-bottom: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
.cruise-entry:hover { background: #fdf9f5; }
.cruise-entry.cancelled { opacity: 0.65; }
.cruise-date {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cardinal);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.cruise-entry i { font-style: italic; }
.cruise-entry b { color: var(--ink); }
.cruise-entry a { color: var(--cardinal); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; }
.cruise-entry a:hover { border-color: var(--cardinal); }

/* ── SIDEBAR ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.sidebar > * { margin-bottom: 36px; }
.sidebar > *:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
.card-head { padding: 14px 18px; }
.card-head.dark { background: var(--ink); }
.card-head.ocean { background: var(--pacific); }
.card-head h3 {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff;
}
.card-body { padding: 18px; }

.stat-row {
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
  padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); gap: 10px;
}
.stat-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.stat-lbl {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-light); flex-shrink: 0;
}
.stat-val { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink); text-align: right; }

.edu-item { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.edu-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.edu-deg { font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--cardinal); margin-bottom: 1px; }
.edu-field { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 2px; }
.edu-inst { font-size: 12.5px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-light); }

.pull-quote {
  background: var(--cardinal);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 26px 22px;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.pull-quote::before {
  content: '"'; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 150px; line-height: 1; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  position: absolute; top: -18px; left: 8px; pointer-events: none;
}
.pull-quote p {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 15px; font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  line-height: 1.6; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0 !important;
}

/* ── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.page-footer {
  background: var(--ink);
  padding: 28px 32px;
}
.footer-inner {
  max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  padding-top: 20px;
}
.footer-inner p {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin: 0;
}
.footer-inner a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
.footer-inner a:hover { color: var(--gold-light); }
.footer-hash {
  font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  letter-spacing: 0.25em;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 12px 0 0;
  max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 920px) {
  .hero-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .hero-photo { width: 140px; height: 140px; }
  .hero-photo-accent { width: 140px; height: 140px; }
  .page-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
  .interests-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  .cruise-entry { grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr; }
}
@media (max-width: 560px) {
  .interests-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .tl-item { grid-template-columns: 68px 1fr; }
  .cruise-entry { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-stripe"></div>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <span class="chico-wordmark">California State University, <span>Chico</span></span>
    <div class="hdr-div"></div>
    <span class="dept-label">Department of Anthropology</span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-photo-wrap">
      <div class="hero-photo-accent"></div>
      <img class="hero-photo" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Dr. Charles F. Urbanowicz">
    </div>
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Professor Emeritus of Anthropology</p>
      <h1 class="hero-name">Dr. Charles F. Urbanowicz</h1>
      <p class="hero-title">Retired Professor <em>Emeritus</em> of Anthropology<br>California State University Chico / Chico, California 95929-0400</p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span class="meta-item">Anthropology Department: Phone: 530-898-6192</span>
        <span class="meta-item">email: <a href="mailto:curbanowicz@csuchico.edu">curbanowicz@csuchico.edu</a> [or] <a href="mailto:csurbanowicz@gmail.com">csurbanowicz@gmail.com</a></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-wave">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 72" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0,72 L0,36 C150,0 300,65 450,36 C600,8 750,65 900,36 C1050,8 1150,50 1200,36 L1200,72 Z" fill="#FAF7F2"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DATE + RETIREMENT NOTICE -->
<div class="date-banner">
  <p><strong>15 April 2026</strong></p>
</div>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<div class="page-wrap">
<main>

  <!-- Retirement notice -->
  <div class="retirement-notice">
    On 31 December 2009 I retired from California State University Chico and am now associated with the University as a Professor Emeritus of Anthropology.
  </div>

  <!-- VITAL STATISTICS -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Personal</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Vital Statistics</h2>
    <p><b>Born:</b> September <b>1942</b> (Jersey City, New Jersey)<br>
    <b>Married:</b> December <b>1963</b><br>
    <b>One Child:</b> Born October <b>1972</b> (Married April <b>1993</b>)<br>
    <b>Two Grandchildren:</b> Born May <b>1996</b> and February <b>1998</b>)<br>
    <b>Two GreatGrandchildren:</b> Born September <b>2023</b> and June <b>2025</b></p>
  </section>

  <!-- EDUCATION -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Credentials</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Education Summary</h2>
    <p><b>Ph.D.</b> <b>1972</b> Anthropology, University of Oregon, Eugene, Oregon.<br>
    <b>M. A.</b> <b>1969</b> Anthropology, University of Oregon, Eugene, Oregon.<br>
    <b>B. A</b>. <b>1967</b> Sociology-Anthropology, Western Washington University, Bellingham, Washington.<br>
    <b>Military Service:</b> United States Air Force (<b>1961-&gt;1965</b>), Honorable Discharge<br>
    <b>1960-&gt;1961}</b> Course Work at New York University, New York City.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ACADEMIC APPOINTMENTS -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Career</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Academic Appointments</h2>
    <p>Professor <em>Emeritus</em> of Anthropology (<b>2005 to the present</b>)<br>
    Associate Dean, Regional and Continuing Education, CSU, Chico <b>(1977-&gt;1988)</b><br>
    Social Science Coordinator, CSU, Chico <b>(1975-&gt;1977)</b><br>
    Anthropology Faculty Member at CSU, Chico <b>(1973 to the present)</b><br>
    Assistant Professor of Anthropology, University of Minnesota, Minneapolis, MN <b>(1972-&gt;1973)</b></p>
  </section>

  <!-- TEACHING AND RELATED ACTIVITIES -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">History</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Teaching and Related Activities at California State University, Chico</h2>
    <p>Joined the faculty of California State University, Chico in August <b>1973</b> and retired in May <b>2005</b> and colleagues gave me the title of Professor <em>Emeritus</em> of Anthropology. The California State University System had a phased retirement program known as <b>FERP</b> (<b>F</b>aculty <b>E</b>arly <b>R</b>etirement <b>P</b>rogram) and I participated in this, teaching every fall semester for five years, until <b>December 2009</b> when I completely retired from CSU, Chico.</p>
    <p>Over the years <b>1975-&gt;1977</b> was the Social Science Coordinator for the College of Behavioral and Social Sciences. In <b>1977</b> was granted tenure and was promoted to Associate Professor and in Fall <b>1977</b> became the Associate Dean in The Center for Regional and Continuing Education at CSU, Chico, a position held from <b>1977-to-1988.</b> In <b>1982</b> was promoted to Professor of Anthropology.</p>
    <p>In July <b>1988</b> resigned from my Administrative position and returned to full-time teaching in Fall <b>1989</b>. In <b>1994</b> students selected me for Honorary Membership in the Chico Chapter of <em>Phi Eta Sigma</em> (National Honor Society) and for the years <b>1997-to-1999</b> was selected to be one of five "Master Teachers" of California State University, Chico. In <b>2001</b> students selected me for Honorary Membership in the <em>Alpha Alpha Mu</em> Chapter of <em>Alpha Psi Omega</em> (National Theatre Honor Society). In December <b>2009</b> completed my five-year participation in <b>FERP</b> and am completely retired and no longer teach at California State University, Chico. For a <b>complete</b> "Reverse Chronological Order" of <b>all</b> Papers, Publications, Performances, and Professional Activities <b>since 1965</b> to the present, <b>please see</b> <a href="https://curbanowicz.yourweb.csuchico.edu/ReverseChronOrder.html">https://curbanowicz.yourweb.csuchico.edu/ReverseChronOrder.html</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- CRUISE OVERVIEW -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">At Sea</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Cruise Lectures Overview</h2>
    <p>Since <b>2004</b> have made presentations on various cruises, with emphasis on "<b>Peoples and Cultures of the Pacific</b>" as well as <b>World War II</b>. Since <b>2009</b>, my wife Carol ("Sadie") Urbanowicz, has also made numerous presentations on various cruises. PowerPoint presentations that I have made on selected cruise itineraries have also included lectures dealing with <b>Paul Gauguin</b>, <b>Charles Darwin</b> as well as <b>Science, Technology, and Creativity</b>. I have lectured on itineraries of the following ships and in alphabetical order they are: <em>Amsterdam</em> (<b>2008</b>, <b>2013, 2015, &amp; 2016</b>), <em>Maasdam</em> (<b>2018a</b> &amp; <b>2018b</b>), <em>Noordam</em> (<b>2016</b>), <em>Ocean Princess</em> (<b>2015</b>) (<b>note</b>: formerly known as the <em>Tahitian Princess</em>), <em>Oosterdam</em> (<b>2012</b>), <em>Pacific Princess</em> (<b>2006</b>), <em>Paul Gauguin</em> (<b>2007, 2016</b>, <b>2017</b>, <b>2022a &amp; 2022b</b>), <em>Prinsendam</em> (<b>2009</b>), <em>Queen Elizabeth</em> (<b>2012</b>), <em>Queen Elizabeth 2</em> (<b>2007</b>), <em>Queen Victoria</em> (<b>2011</b>), <em>Rhapsody of the Seas</em> (<b>2011</b>), <em>Rotterdam</em> (<b>2010</b>), <em>Ryndam</em> (<b>2008</b>), <em>Sapphire Princess</em> (<b>2007</b> &amp; <b>2014</b>), <em>Seabourn Sojourn</em> (<b>2017 &amp; 2018</b>), <em>Spirit of Oceanus</em> (<b>2009</b>), <em>Star Princess</em> (<b>2012</b>), <em>Statendam</em> (<b>2013</b>, <b>2014, &amp; 2015</b>), <em>Tahitian Princess</em> (<b>2004</b> &amp; <b>2005</b>) (<b>note</b>: now known as the <em>Ocean Princess</em>), <em>Viking Sun</em> (<b>2018 &amp; 2020</b>), <em>Volendam</em> (<b>2010</b> &amp; <b>2014</b>), and <em>Zaandam</em> (<b>2008</b> &amp; <b>2011</b>). In <b>2016</b> and in <b>2017</b> I was designated a "<a href="http://www.smithsonianjourneys.org/experts/charles-urbanowicz/">Smithsonian Journeys Expert</a>" for the <em>Paul Gauguin</em> on a "Voyage" to French Polynesia. In <b>June 2022</b> I provided lectures on the first ever "Chairman's Cruise" on the <em>Le Paul Gauguin</em> in French Polynesia and in <b>September 2022</b> I was a Smithsonian Journeys Expert for a "Cruising French Polynesia" cruise on the <em>Le Paul Gauguin</em>.</p>
  </section>

